                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18250915-280-victim1403 t18250915-280-viclabel1502"></join>. On the 4th of July, between ten and eleven o'clock in the morning, I was in <placeName id="t18250915-280-crimeloc1503">Saffron-hill</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18250915-280-crimeloc1503" type="placeName" value="Saffron-hill"></interp>
