                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18250915-280-off1500 t18250915-280-crimeloc1503"></join>; I felt a little pull at my pocket, and missed my handkerchief; I turned round, and the prisoner was close at my heels - I said he had picked my pocket; he said he had not; I said, "It is of no use to deny it." I put his arm aside, and found my handkerchief under his arm.</p>
               <p>The prisoner pleaded distress.</p>
